#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:53
#, no-c-format
msgid "Introduction"
msgstr "Uvod"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:55
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&kiten; is a set of 3 tools with multiple functions. Firstly, it is a "
"convenient English to Japanese and Japanese to English dictionary; secondly, "
"it is a Kanji dictionary, with multiple ways to look up specific characters; "
"thirdly, it is a tool to help you learn Kanji."
msgstr ""
"&kiten; je komplet 3 orodij z več funkcijami. Prvič, to je priročen angleško-"
"japonski in japonsko-angleški slovar; drugič, to je slovar Kanji, z več "
"načini za iskanje določenih znakov; tretjič, je orodje, ki vam pomaga pri "
"učenju Kanjija."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:61
#, no-c-format
msgid "Each of these modes is discussed in its own chapter."
msgstr "Vsak od teh načinov je obravnavan v svojem poglavju."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:64
#, no-c-format
msgid "Here's a screenshot of &kiten;"
msgstr "Tukaj je posnetek zaslona &kiten;"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:67
#, no-c-format
msgid "&kiten; screenshot"
msgstr "&kiten; posnetek zaslona"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:74
#, no-c-format
msgid "Using the Dictionary"
msgstr "Uporaba slovarja"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:76
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&kiten;'s most basic mode is as a dictionary for looking up both English and "
"Japanese words. You can also add other dictionaries to &kiten;'s list."
msgstr ""
"Najosnovnejši način &kiten; je kot slovar za iskanje angleških in japonskih "
"besed. Na seznam &kiten; lahko dodate tudi druge slovarje."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:80
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&kiten; uses Jim Breen's Edict and Kanjidic as the default dictionaries. You "
"can find more information at <ulink url=\"https://www.edrdg.org/jmdict/edict."
"html\">the Edict web site</ulink> and <ulink url=\"https://www.edrdg.org/"
"wiki/index.php/KANJIDIC_Project\">the Kanjidic web site</ulink>."
msgstr ""
"&kiten; kot privzeta slovarja uporablja Edict in Kanjidic Jima Breena. Več "
"informacij najdete na <ulink url=\"https://www.edrdg.org/jmdict/edict.html"
"\">spletnem mestu Edict</ulink> in <ulink url=\"https://www.edrdg. org/wiki/"
"index.php/KANJIDIC_Project\">spletnem mestu Kanjidic</ulink>."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:83
#, no-c-format
msgid "Looking Up Words"
msgstr "Iskanje besed"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:85
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To look up words in either language, type them in to the text-edit (much "
"like &konqueror;'s location bar) and press either &Enter; or the "
"<guibutton>Search</guibutton> button on the toolbar (again, much like "
"&konqueror;). &kiten; will then look up the word."
msgstr ""
"Če želite poiskati besede v katerem koli jeziku, jih vnesite v polje za "
"urejanje besedila (podobno kot lokacijska vrstica &konqueror;) in pritisnite "
"bodisi &Enter; ali gumb <guibutton>Išči</guibutton> v orodni vrstici (spet "
"podobno kot &konqueror;). &kiten; bo nato poiskal besedo."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:91
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can enter Kanji, Kana and English and get back results from &kiten;. "
"These results of your search will appear in the large results view which "
"takes up the majority of the &kiten; window."
msgstr ""
"Vnesete lahko Kanji, Kana in angleščino in dobite nazaj rezultate iz "
"&kiten;. Ti rezultati vašega iskanja bodo prikazani v velikem pogledu "
"rezultatov, ki zavzame večine okna &kiten;."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:96
#, no-c-format
msgid "searching for an English translation"
msgstr "iskanje angleškega prevoda"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:99
#, no-c-format
msgid "&kiten; search screenshot"
msgstr "&kiten; iskalni posnetek zaslona"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:104
#, no-c-format
msgid "Filtering"
msgstr "Filtriranje"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:106
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Often times you will want to filter rare words from your search. &kiten; "
"will do this for you if toggle <menuchoice><guimenu>Search</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>Filter Out Rare</guimenuitem></menuchoice>."
msgstr ""
"Pogosto boste želeli iz svojega iskanja filtrirati redke besede. &kiten; bo "
"to naredil namesto vas, če preklopite <menuchoice><guimenu>Iskanje</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>Izloči redke</guimenuitem></menuchoice>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:111
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Not all dictionary files support filtering rare entries - most dictionaries, "
"excluding the two provided by default in &kiten; do not."
msgstr ""
"Vse slovarske datoteke ne podpirajo filtriranja redkih vnosov - večina "
"slovarjev, razen dveh, ki sta privzeto na voljo v &kiten; ne."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:116
#, no-c-format
msgid "Screenshot using filtering of rare words"
msgstr "Posnetek zaslona s filtriranjem redkih besed"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:119
#, no-c-format
msgid "&kiten; filtering search"
msgstr "&kiten; filtriranje iskanja"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:126
#, no-c-format
msgid "Common/Uncommon words"
msgstr "Običajne/neobičajne besede"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:127
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Another way to separate information is to filter common and uncommon words, "
"this is useful when you want to focus on the common words and/or have "
"interest on uncommon ones. The only difference between Filter Out Rare and "
"Common/Uncommon options is that here you also get the Rare/Uncommon results."
msgstr ""
"Drug način za ločevanje informacij je filtriranje običajnih in neobičajnih "
"besed. To je uporabno, ko se želite osredotočiti na pogoste besede in/ali "
"vas zanimajo neobičajne. Edina razlika med možnostma Fitriraj redke in "
"Običajne/Neobičajne je, da tukaj dobite tudi rezultate Redke/Neobičajne."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:133
#, no-c-format
msgid "Screenshot for match common/uncommon"
msgstr "Posnetek zaslona za ujemanje običajno/neobičajno"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:136
#, no-c-format
msgid "&kiten; match common/uncommon"
msgstr "&kiten; ujemanje običajno/neobičajno"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:145
#, no-c-format
msgid "Advanced Searches"
msgstr "Napredna iskanja"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:147
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&kiten; supports more advanced searches than plain normal word searches."
msgstr "&kiten; podpira bolj napredna iskanja kot običajna iskanja besed."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:151
#, no-c-format
msgid "Beginning/Ending/Anywhere Searches"
msgstr "Začetek/konec/iskanja kjer koli"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:152
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Beside a search with <guilabel>Exact Match</guilabel> &kiten; has three "
"additional search modes."
msgstr ""
"Poleg iskanja z <guilabel>natančnim ujemanjem</guilabel> &kiten; ima tri "
"dodatne načine iskanja."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:154
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To search for the beginning of a word, instead of pressing the "
"<guibutton>Search</guibutton> button on the toolbar or pressing &Enter; on "
"the text-entry in the toolbar, choose using the <menuchoice><guimenu>Search</"
"guimenu><guisubmenu>Match Type </guisubmenu><guimenuitem>Match Beginning</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice>. Similarly, for ending or anywhere searches, "
"choose <menuchoice><guimenu>Search</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Match Type</"
"guisubmenu></menuchoice> <guimenuitem>Match Anywhere</guimenuitem> or "
"<guimenuitem>Match Ending</guimenuitem> to search for your text anywhere in "
"or at the end of a word. These search modes work for searches of both "
"languages."
msgstr ""
"Če želite poiskati začetek besede, namesto da pritisnete gumb "
"<guibutton>Išči</guibutton> v orodni vrstici ali pritisnete &Enter; pri "
"vnosu besedila v orodni vrstici izberite s pomočjo "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Iskanja</guimenu><guisubmenu>Vrsta ujemanja </"
"guisubmenu><guimenuitem>Ujemanje začetka</guimenuitem></menuchoice>. Podobno "
"za iskanja na koncu ali kjer koli izberite <menuchoice><guimenu>Išči</"
"guimenu> <guisubmenu>Vrsto ujemanja</guisubmenu></menuchoice> "
"<guimenuitem>Ujemanje kjer koli</guimenuitem> ali <guimenuitem>Ujemanja "
"konca</guimenuitem> za iskanje besedila kjer koli v ali na koncu besede. Ti "
"načini iskanja delujejo pri iskanju v obeh jezikih."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:166
#, no-c-format
msgid "Screenshot for match ending search"
msgstr "Posnetek zaslona za iskanje ujemanja konca"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:169
#, no-c-format
msgid "&kiten; match ending search"
msgstr "&kiten; ujemanje pri iskanju konca"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:176
#, no-c-format
msgid "Word type searches"
msgstr "Iskanje besednih vrst"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:177
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&kiten; supports word type searches such as: verb, noun, adjective, adverb, "
"prefix, suffix, expression or any type. This way you can filter your results "
"more conveniently."
msgstr ""
"&kiten; podpira iskanje besednih vrst, kot so: glagol, samostalnik, "
"pridevnik, prislov, predpona, pripona, izraz ali katera koli vrsta. Tako "
"lahko bolj priročno filtrirate rezultate."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:182
#, no-c-format
msgid "Screenshot for match word type"
msgstr "Posnetek zaslona za besedno vrsto ujemanja"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:185
#, no-c-format
msgid "&kiten; match word type"
msgstr "&kiten; ujemanje besedne vrste"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:192
#, no-c-format
msgid "Searching in Results"
msgstr "Iskanje v rezultatih"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:194
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&kiten; can also help you refine your searches by allowing you to search for "
"new text in the results generated by a previous search. To do this, just "
"choose <menuchoice><guimenu>Search</guimenu><guimenuitem>Search in Results</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice> to perform your search. Similarly to beginning/"
"ending/anywhere searches, this works for both languages too."
msgstr ""
"&kiten; vam lahko tudi pomaga izboljšati iskanja, tako da vam omogoči "
"iskanje novega besedila v rezultatih prejšnjega iskanja. Če želite to "
"narediti, preprosto izberite <menuchoice><guimenu>Iskanje</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>Iskanje v rezultatih</guimenuitem></menuchoice> za "
"izvedbo iskanja. Podobno kot iskanja na začetku/koncu/kjer koli, tudi to "
"deluje za oba jezika."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:202
#, no-c-format
msgid "Screenshot for search in results"
msgstr "Posnetek zaslona za iskanje v rezultatih"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:205
#, no-c-format
msgid "&kiten; search in results"
msgstr "&kiten; iskanje v rezultatih"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:236
#, no-c-format
msgid "Looking Up Kanji"
msgstr "Iskanje Kanjijev"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:238
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&kiten; has features that makes finding the one kanji you want easy from "
"over 14,000 in the default dictionary."
msgstr ""
"&kiten; ima funkcije, ki olajšajo iskanje želenega Kanjija med več kot "
"14.000 v privzetem slovarju."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:241
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Clicking on any Kanji in the main result view will show details on that "
"particular Kanji. This can sometimes be the fastest way to look up a Kanji."
msgstr ""
"Če kliknete kateri koli kanji v glavnem pogledu rezultatov, se prikažejo "
"podrobnosti o tem določenem Kanjiju. Včasih je to lahko najhitrejši način za "
"iskanje Kanjija."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:245
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Kanji searches are also filtered according to whether "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Search</guimenu><guimenuitem>Filter Out Rare</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice> is checked."
msgstr ""
"Iskanja Kanji so prav tako filtrirana glede na to, ali je potrjena možnost "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Iskanje</guimenu><guimenuitem>Izloči redke</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice>."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:250
#, no-c-format
msgid "Regular Searching"
msgstr "Redno iskanje"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:252
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can search with English and Japanese search strings the exact same way "
"you can with the normal dictionary."
msgstr ""
"Iščete lahko z angleškimi in japonskimi iskalnimi nizi na popolnoma enak "
"način kot z običajnim slovarjem."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:258
#, no-c-format
msgid "Radical Searching"
msgstr "Radikalno iskanje"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:260
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can use &kiten;'s radical search dialog to search for Kanji with a "
"combination of radicals and a certain stroke count. Choose "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Search</guimenu><guimenuitem>Radical Selector</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice> to open the radical search dialog."
msgstr ""
"Pogovorno okno radikalnega iskanja &kiten; lahko uporabite za iskanje "
"kanjijev s kombinacijo radikalov in določenega števila potez. Izberite "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Iskanje</guimenu><guimenuitem>Radikalni izbirnik</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice>, da odprete pogovorno okno radikalnega iskanja."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:266
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To choose the radicals you want to be in your Kanji, select one them from "
"the buttons at the bottom of the window. To display possible radicals to "
"select from this buttons with a certain number of strokes, choose this "
"number of strokes from the spinboxes just above the buttons. The radicals "
"you choose will appear in the listbox at the top."
msgstr ""
"Če želite izbrati radikale, za katere želite, da so v vašem Kanjiju, "
"izberite enega izmed gumbov na dnu okna. Če želite prikazati možne radikale "
"za izbiro med temi gumbi z določenim številom potez, izberite to število "
"potez v vrtilnih poljih tik nad gumbi. Izbrani radikali se bodo pojavili v "
"seznamskem polju na vrhu."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:272
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To choose how many strokes your Kanji should have, just enter the values "
"into the spin boxes below the results area."
msgstr ""
"Če želite izbrati, koliko potez naj ima vaš Kanji, preprosto vnesite "
"vrednosti v vrtilna polja pod območjem z rezultati."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:275
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To perform the lookup, press the button that matches the kanji you wanted to "
"look up."
msgstr ""
"Če želite izvesti iskanje, pritisnite gumb, ki se ujema s Kanjijem, ki ste "
"ga želeli poiskati."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:279
#, no-c-format
msgid "Screenshot for radical selector"
msgstr "Posnetek zaslona za radikalni izbirnik"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:282
#, no-c-format
msgid "&kiten; radical selector"
msgstr "&kiten; radikalni selektor"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:289
#, no-c-format
msgid "Grade Search"
msgstr "Iskanje ocen"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:291
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To get a list of all Kanji in a certain grade, enter that into the search "
"box as \"G:1\" (G: is the Kanjidic tag for grade)."
msgstr ""
"Če želite dobiti seznam vseh Kanjijev v določenem razredu, ga vnesite v "
"iskalno polje kot \"G:1\" (G: je kanjidska oznaka za razred)."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:295
#, no-c-format
msgid "Screenshot for kanji grade search"
msgstr "Posnetek zaslona za iskanje stopnje kanji"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:298
#, no-c-format
msgid "&kiten; kanji grade search"
msgstr "&kiten; iskanje stopnje kanji"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:305
#, no-c-format
msgid "Stroke Search"
msgstr "Iskanje potez"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:307
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To get a list of all Kanji with a certain number of strokes, enter that "
"number the search box as \"S:2\"."
msgstr ""
"Če želite dobiti seznam vseh kanjijev z določenim številom potez, vnesite to "
"številko v iskalno polje kot \"S:2\"."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:311
#, no-c-format
msgid "Screenshot for kanji strokes search"
msgstr "Posnetek zaslona za iskanje črt kanji"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:314
#, no-c-format
msgid "&kiten; kanji strokes search"
msgstr "&kiten; iskanje črt kanji"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:321
#, no-c-format
msgid "Kanji List"
msgstr "Seznam Kanji"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:323
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This part of the Kanji Browser lets you visualize a list of kanji filtered "
"by grade and number of strokes. By Clicking on a kanji you can get detailed "
"information about it. Kanji Browser separates the list in Jouyou, Jinmeiyou "
"and non-Jouyou kanji. All this kanji is available thanks to the KANJIDIC "
"dictionary."
msgstr ""
"Ta del brskalnika Kanji vam omogoča vizualizacijo seznama kanjijev, "
"filtriranih po stopnji in številu potez. S klikom na Kanji lahko dobite "
"podrobne informacije o njem. Brskalnk Kanji loči seznam Kanji Jouyou, "
"Jinmeiyou in ne-Jouyou. Vsi ti Kanji so na voljo zahvaljujoč slovarju "
"KANJIDIC."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:330
#, no-c-format
msgid "Screenshot for kanji list"
msgstr "Posnetek zaslona za seznam kanji"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:333
#, no-c-format
msgid "&kiten; kanji list"
msgstr "&kiten; seznam kanji"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:340
#, no-c-format
msgid "Kanji Information"
msgstr "Kanji informacije"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:342
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This part shows you detailed information about a kanji such as: kanji stroke "
"order, number of strokes, readings and meanings."
msgstr ""
"Ta del prikazuje podrobne informacije o kanjiju, kot so: vrstni red potez "
"kanjijev, število potez, odčitki in pomeni."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:346
#, no-c-format
msgid "Screenshot for kanji information"
msgstr "Posnetek zaslona za informacije o kanjiju"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:349
#, no-c-format
msgid "&kiten; kanji information"
msgstr "&kiten; kanji informacije"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:358
#, no-c-format
msgid "Miscellaneous"
msgstr "Razno"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:360
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This chapter describes miscellaneous features that can be used in both modes "
"in &kiten;'s main window."
msgstr ""
"V tem poglavju so opisane različne funkcije, ki jih je mogoče uporabiti v "
"obeh načinih v glavnem oknu &kiten;."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:364
#, no-c-format
msgid "History"
msgstr "Zgodovina"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:366
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&kiten; keeps track of all of your queries in the input field. You can see "
"your last results by clicking on the check mark at the right of the input "
"field. To go forward one in the history, choose <menuchoice><guimenu>Go</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>Forward</guimenuitem></menuchoice>. To go backward one "
"in the history, choose <menuchoice><guimenu>Go</guimenu><guimenuitem>Back</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice>."
msgstr ""
"&kiten; spremlja vse vaše poizvedbe v vnosnem polju. Svoje zadnje rezultate "
"si lahko ogledate s klikom na kljukico na desni strani vnosnega polja. Če se "
"želite pomakniti naprej v zgodovini, izberite <menuchoice><guimenu>Pojdi</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>Naprej</guimenuitem></menuchoice>. Če se želite vrniti "
"nazaj v zgodovini, izberite <menuchoice><guimenu>Pojdi</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>Nazaj</guimenuitem></menuchoice>."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:376
#, no-c-format
msgid "Fonts"
msgstr "Pisave"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:378
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can choose the font that &kiten; uses in its result view. Go to the "
"&kiten; configuration dialog, which can be opened by choosing "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Settings</guimenu><guimenuitem>Configure &kiten;...</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice>. Select the <guilabel>Font</guilabel> page of the "
"dialog and select the font in the font-chooser."
msgstr ""
"Izberete lahko pisavo, ki jo &kiten; uporablja v pogledu rezultatov. Pojdite "
"na &kiten; konfiguracijsko pogovorno okno, ki ga lahko odprete z izbiro "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Nastavitve</guimenu><guimenuitem>Konfiguriraj &kiten;..."
"</guimenuitem></menuchoice>. Izberite stran <guilabel>Pisava</guilabel> v "
"pogovornem oknu in izberite pisavo v izbirniku pisav."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:386
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&Qt; 's font-substitution system makes it so a Japanese font will always be "
"substituted for Japanese characters, even if the font you specify doesn't "
"include them. Thus, you can choose any font in the chooser and everything "
"should still display fine."
msgstr ""
"&Qt; sistem zamenjave pisav omogoča, da bo japonska pisava vedno nadomeščena "
"z japonskimi znaki, tudi če jih pisava, ki jo podate, ne vključuje. Tako "
"lahko v izbirniku izberete katero koli pisavo in vse bi moralo biti "
"prikazano v redu."

